0.body: The pen tool is a multi-tool for a variety of tasks, and an incubator for new capabilities. Scripted drawing to PNG images using the JavaFX GraphicsContext Scripted drawing to monospaced text, for output to the terminal Working with fictional calendar systems Working with "historical" events and timelines Some of these features, once mature, will become part of the Joe language's standard library.
0.title: Introduction to Pen

7.body: TextCanvas is a canvas for drawing diagrams using monospaced text for output to the terminal. It can be thought of as a two-dimensional array of character cells, with (0,0) at the top-left with columns extending to the left and rows extending down. Characters and strings can be inserted at any ( column , row ) cell; the canvas will expand automatically.
